Setup Instructions
==================

Server-side setup
----------------------------
1. Install PHP 5.1.0 or greater (http://php.net/manual/en/install.php)
2. Install SQLite (http://www.sqlite.org/download.html)
3. Download the Yii framework (http://www.yiiframework.com/download), and extract it to `yii-highcharts/yii`

Client-side setup
-----------------
1. Install bower (http://bower.io)
2. From the same folder that contains `bower.json`, run the following command to install any necessary JavaScript packages:

    bower install

Running the examples
--------------------
1. Run the following from `yii-highcharts`

    php -S localhost:8080
    
2. Visit `http://localhost:8080/example_app`
